	<a href="http://edudemic.com/2012/10/the-20-best-learning-management-systems/">20 best LMS</a></p>
<p>
	From Moodle to Edmodo to Inquisiq r3, there&rsquo;s a lot of tools you can use to manage, track, and deliver courses and training programs in your school. They&rsquo;re called Learning Management Solutions (LMS) or sometimes Learning Management Systems. Either way, how do you pick which is the best? A new infographic from Capterra spells it out in simple stats.</p>
<p>
	See Also: A Quick Guide To Learning Management Systems</p>
<p>
	Key Takeaways</p>
<ul>
	<li>
		The LMS industry is now a billion dollar plus industry.</li>
	<li>
		There are hundreds of LMS solutions out there.</li>
	<li>
		Moodle, Edmodo, and Blackboard are the big names in the industry.</li>
	<li>
		The most popular tool is not the most popular on social media. See: Edmodo vs Moodle</li>
</ul> 
